  "title": "In/Visible — The Idunnos",
  "summary": "“‘The Idunnos,’ which I generated using Midjourney, shows beings that reside in between the nexus of everything and nothing. They stand as gatekeepers in the liminal space where light meets darkness, where silence meets sound, where the known and the unknown converge. They are the personification of the question mark, the embodiment of the undefined, the representatives of the unanswerable.” — Jah",
